    "description": "<strong>Journey Express</strong> is a hybrid 2D/3D adventure game that challenges you to get a party of travelers from their current home to a new life elsewhere. The road is fraught with dangers, and you must carefully manage food, medicine, and money so that you and your party survives.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE</h2><br>While traveling a world handmade in pixel art, explore it freely in 1st-person! Acquire food and other items by hunting, fishing, and searching for valuables. <br><br>Dynamic time of day, weather, and seasons change how fast you're able to progress, affect your party's morale, and influence the events you encounter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127350/extras/b2e7850c52762e2122136a63641d2ff5.poster.avif?t=1772038507\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127350/extras/b2e7850c52762e2122136a63641d2ff5.webm?t=1772038507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127350/extras/b2e7850c52762e2122136a63641d2ff5.mp4?t=1772038507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PROGRESSION</h2><br>Your family's name isn't what it used to be. Generations of scoundrels and swindlers have left it tarnished, but each of your completed journeys will contribute to your wealth and reputation. <br><br>If your character succumbs to injury or illness, you will create a new one as a successor to continue where they left off.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127350/extras/b7f22f91687058f1ca167248a478045b.poster.avif?t=1772038507\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127350/extras/b7f22f91687058f1ca167248a478045b.webm?t=1772038507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127350/extras/b7f22f91687058f1ca167248a478045b.mp4?t=1772038507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAP &amp; DISCOVERIES</h2><br>Freely decide what direction you go at any time while you manage your food and supplies to safely get where you want to go. Navigate grasslands, mountains, deserts, and more!<br><br>Find unique locations and discoveries scattered across the land for additional money and reputation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127350/extras/537bda5b42c229dd87cff4ed45887ed9.poster.avif?t=1772038507\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127350/extras/537bda5b42c229dd87cff4ed45887ed9.webm?t=1772038507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127350/extras/537bda5b42c229dd87cff4ed45887ed9.mp4?t=1772038507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
